Well, that's just the thing,
detective.

508
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:37,000
We can't be certain it ever will.

509
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:41,680
Imagine the thing you fear
most in the world.

510
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:45,840
Imagine that's all you see.

511
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:48,080
Every waking hour.

512
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:09,760
No. No. No!

